SUMMARY:Tommy Davidson LIVE at Brea Improv
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260702T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you
	 purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Ti
	ckets (Ticketmaster) \nResale Tickets (VividSeats) \nTommy Davidson LIVE a
	t Brea Improv\nComedy legend Tommy Davidson brings his exceptional stand-u
	p comedy to the Brea Improv for a multi-night run in July 2026. \nBest kno
	wn as one of the stars of the hit TV show In Living Color\, Tommy Davidson
	 is a versatile entertainer whose range spans stand-up\, acting\, and musi
	c. \nEvent Details\nDate: Thursday\, July 2\, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM PDT (Doo
	rs open at 6:30 PM)\nVenue: Brea Improv\nAddress: 180 S Brea Blvd\, Brea\,
	 CA 92821\nAge Requirement: 21+\nSeating: General Admission\, first-come f
	irst-served\nNote: Two-item minimum purchase required \nAbout Tommy Davids
	on\nTommy Davidson is best known as one of the original cast members of In
	 Living Color\, where his impressions of Sammy Davis Jr. and Michael Jacks
	on became iconic. He has starred in Disney’s The Proud Family\, appeared i
	n films like Ace Ventura II and Bamboozled\, and continues to headline maj
	or comedy venues across the country. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHigh-energy stand
	-up from an In Living Color legend\nHilarious impressions and character wo
	rk\nIntimate club setting at the Brea Improv\nVIP seating options availabl
	e\n21+ show with full bar and two-item minimum\n\nVenue Information\nBrea 
	Improv is located at 180 S Brea Blvd in Brea\, CA. Part of the legendary I
	mprov comedy club chain in Orange County\, CA. \nTicket Information\nTicke
	ts start at $25 (plus fees). VIP from $40. GA Booths from $75. VIP Premium
	 Booths from $90. \nOfficial Tickets (Ticketmaster) \nResale Tickets (Vivi
	dSeats) \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you 
	purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales ar
	e final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for 
	entry.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/tommy-davidson-live-at-brea-imp
	rov/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/tommy-davidson-live-at-brea-improv/
LOCATION:Brea Improv\, 180 South Brea Blvd\, Brea\, CA\, 92821\, United Sta
	tes
