SUMMARY:Wingman THURSDAY Miami’s Social Comedy Show
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260702T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:One night only on a Thursday! Meet new people\, laugh with frie
	nds\, enjoy cocktails\, and experience Miami's most social comedy show.\n\
	n\nNOTE: This is a one-time THURSDAY event this week. This show is weekly 
	on Wednesdays! \nA fun night out where people happen to meet. \nWingman TH
	URSDAY is Miami’s social comedy show where dating\, relationships\, and mo
	dern romance become the night’s entertainment. Hosted by Miami’s Best Come
	dian Manny Garavito and Miami’s Best Master of Ceremonies Luke Prince\, th
	e show stirs up live comedy\, tasteful crowd interaction\, audience storie
	s\, terrible dating advice\, red flags\, green flags\, first dates on the 
	spot\, and the hilarious realities of navigating Miami’s social scene. \nW
	hether you’re single\, taken\, in the alphabet\, somewhere in between\, or
	 just here to watch the tea spill\, you’ll be part of a night filled with 
	laughs\, unexpected moments\, and real conversations. Audience participati
	on is encouraged but never required\, making it just as fun to watch as it
	 is to jump in. \nBring your friends\, your situationships\, your worst da
	ting stories\, but most importantly your sense of humor. \nLadies drink fr
	ee during the beginning of showtime from 9 PM to 10 PM. \nComedy. Cocktail
	s. Questionable decisions. \nTopics include but are not limited to: \n\nBr
	ickell finance bros\nYacht season\nSugar daddy retirement plans\nInstagram
	 followers\n“What do you do?” stress tests\nPenthouse with air matresses\n
	Dating apps\nGym culture\nPlastic surgery\nSpiritual girls\nHow to Ghost 1
	01\nToxic Green Flags\n\n…And enough unsolicited dating advice to keep eve
	ryone single a little longer. \nCome watch. Come participate. Or just sit 
	back and enjoy the turbulence. \nTicket Options \nGeneral Admission (FREE:
	 first come\, first serve)First come\, first served. Whatever seats are no
	t purchased will be available to anyone who arrives early. Once they’re go
	ne\, they’re gone. \n$25 Guaranteed Seating + Wingmen for HireSkip the rus
	h and secure your seats in advance. Plus\, you’ll be guaranteed an opportu
	nity to join Manny and Luke on stage for live crowd interaction\, dating a
	dvice\, matchmaking attempts\, relationship advice\, or whatever romantic 
	turbulence the evening encounters. Limited spots available. \n$50 VIP Flig
	ht Crew Experience (Guaranteed Seating\, Wingmen for Hire\, VIP Bottle Aft
	erparty Access AND Merch)Everything included: guaranteed seating\, Wingman
	 for hire\, access to our bottle section for the afterparty with Manny and
	 Luke\, plus exclusive Miami Comedy merch to take home. VERY Limited spots
	.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/wingman-thursday-miamis-social-comed
	y-show/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/wingman-thursday-miamis-social-comedy-
	show/
LOCATION:Blackbird Ordinary\, Southwest 1st Avenue 729\, Miami\, FL\, 33130
	\, United States
