SUMMARY:Beth Stelling LIVE at Jimmy Kimmel's Comedy Club
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260703T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nAbout the Performer\nBeth Stel
	ling is one of the most celebrated stand-up comedians working today\, know
	n for her razor-sharp wit\, deeply personal storytelling\, and fearless ho
	nesty on stage. \nHer comedy blends confessional vulnerability with biting
	 humor\, tackling topics like relationships\, identity\, and the absurditi
	es of everyday life with a refreshing authenticity. \nStelling has appeare
	d on Netflix\, Comedy Central\, and Late Night with Seth Meyers\, and her 
	acclaimed special Girl Daddy earned widespread critical praise for its emo
	tional depth and comedic precision. \nEvent Details\n\nDate: Friday\, July
	 3\, 2026\nShow Time: 7:30 PM (doors open earlier)\nVenue: Jimmy Kimmel’s 
	Comedy Club\, 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd\, Las Vegas\, NV 89109\nAge Restrictio
	n: 18+ Event\nTicket Prices: From $63\n\nAbout the Venue\nJimmy Kimmel’s C
	omedy Club is one of the premier comedy destinations on the Las Vegas Stri
	p\, located on the iconic LINQ Promenade at 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd. \nThe i
	ntimate venue seats approximately 300 guests and features a state-of-the-a
	rt sound system\, excellent sightlines from every seat\, and a full bar se
	rvice throughout the show. \nThe club’s cozy atmosphere creates an up-clos
	e-and-personal comedy experience unlike the large arena shows Vegas is kno
	wn for. Parking is available at the LINQ Hotel parking garage\, and the ve
	nue is easily accessible via the Las Vegas Monorail. \nThe LINQ Promenade 
	itself offers a variety of dining and entertainment options before and aft
	er the show\, making it a perfect evening destination. \nWhat to Expect\nB
	eth Stelling delivers a headline solo stand-up performance packed with her
	 signature blend of personal storytelling and sharp observational comedy. 
	\nExpect an intimate\, high-energy show where Stelling connects directly w
	ith the audience through her candid\, relatable humor. Her sets are known 
	for building emotional momentum — drawing laughs while also leaving audien
	ces genuinely moved. \nThis is a rare opportunity to see one of comedy’s m
	ost talked-about voices in an intimate Las Vegas club setting. Arrive earl
	y to secure the best seats and enjoy a drink before the show. \nTicket Inf
	ormation\nTickets start from $63 and are available through official and re
	sale channels. \nOfficial TicketsResale Tickets \nThis post contains affil
	iate links. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.\n\nhttps://c
	omedycalendar.com/event/beth-stelling-live-at-jimmys-kimmels-comedy-club/\
	n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/beth-stelling-live-at-jimmys-kimmels-c
	omedy-club/
LOCATION:Jimmy Kimmel’s Comedy Club\, 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd\, Las Vegas\, N
	V\, 89109\, USA
