SUMMARY:Benji Brown LIVE at Arlington Improv (Friday Early Show)
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260703T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate l
	inks. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. \nAbout the Perfor
	mer\nBenji Brown is an urban comedian setting a new standard in comedy. He
	 toured with Martin Lawrence’s 2018 LIT AF Tour in major arenas across the
	 country and is now the host of Martin Lawrence’s “Yall Know What It Is To
	ur.” He headlined his own “Act Crazy If You Want To” national tour in 2019
	\, making him one of the only urban comedians — alongside Kevin Hart — wit
	h the clout to pull off a solo national tour of that magnitude. \nHis vira
	l character KiKi has garnered over 3 million views and helped cement him a
	s one of the next major urban comedic household names. \nEvent Details\nDa
	te: Friday\, July 3\, 2026 \nTime: 7:30 PM (Doors open 6:00 PM) \nVenue: A
	rlington Improv\, 309 Curtis Mathes Way #147\, Arlington\, TX 76018 \nAge 
	Restriction: 18+ \nPrice Range: $20 to $60 per person \nAbout the Venue\nA
	rlington Improv is located in the Highlands Shopping Center in Arlington\,
	 TX\, across from Torchy’s Tacos. It is an intimate comedy club featuring 
	a full bar and restaurant where guests enjoy world-renowned and local comi
	cs in a lively\, up-close setting. \nThe venue also hosts Black Dog Pizza 
	Arcade\, a full-scale free-play retro arcade featuring more than 30 local 
	craft beers. Seating is assigned based on date of purchase. A 2-item food 
	or beverage minimum per person applies once seated\, and there is an 18% s
	ervice charge on all checks in the showroom. \nWhat to Expect\nBenji Brown
	 delivers a full Friday night headlining set at Arlington Improv. Kick off
	 your 4th of July weekend with laughs\, character work\, and the high-ener
	gy delivery that has made Benji one of the most exciting comedians on the 
	national touring circuit. \nThis is an 18+ event. Doors open at 6:00 PM. F
	ood and beverage service ends approximately 45 minutes into the show. All 
	sales are final\, no refunds or exchanges. \nTicket Information\nTickets r
	ange from $20 to $60 per person. Purchase official tickets or find resale 
	options below. \nOfficial TicketsResale Tickets\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.
	com/event/benji-brown-live-at-arlington-improv-friday/\n\nFrom Comedy Cale
	ndar
