SUMMARY:"Weird Al" Yankovic: Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour LIVE at Acrisure Am
	phitheater
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260703T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you
	 purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Ti
	ckets\nResale Tickets \n“Weird Al” Yankovic: Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour LI
	VE at Acrisure Amphitheater\nThe legendary “Weird Al” Yankovic is bringing
	 his highly anticipated  to the Acrisure Amphitheater in Grand Rapids\, Mi
	chigan on July 3\, 2026. With special guest Puddles Pity Party\, this Four
	th of July weekend show promises to be an unforgettable night of comedy\, 
	music\, and pure entertainment. \nEvent Details\nDate: Friday\, July 3\, 2
	026\nTime: 8:00 PM (Doors open earlier)\nVenue: Acrisure Amphitheater\nAdd
	ress: 201 Market Ave SW\, Grand Rapids\, MI 49503\nSpecial Guest: Puddles 
	Pity Party\nAge Requirement: All Ages \nAbout “Weird Al” Yankovic\n“Weird 
	Al” Yankovic is the best-selling comedy recording artist of all time\, kno
	wn for his hilarious parodies of pop hits and original comedy songs spanni
	ng over four decades. With 5 Grammy Awards\, 15 studio albums\, and a care
	er that has made him a cultural icon\, Weird Al continues to delight audie
	nces of all ages with his unique blend of music and comedy. His 2022 biopi
	c WEIRD: The Al Yankovic Story introduced him to a whole new generation of
	 fans. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHilarious parodies of your favorite pop songs p
	erformed live\nElaborate costume changes and theatrical production value\n
	A high-energy\, family-friendly comedy and music extravaganza\nSpecial gue
	st performance by the beloved Puddles Pity Party\nPerfect Fourth of July w
	eekend entertainment for the whole family\nDecades of hits from one of com
	edy’s greatest performers\n\nVenue Information\nAcrisure Amphitheater is G
	rand Rapids’ premier outdoor amphitheater\, located at 201 Market Ave SW i
	n the heart of downtown Grand Rapids\, Michigan. The venue offers excellen
	t sightlines\, great acoustics\, and a fantastic outdoor concert experienc
	e along the Grand River. \nTicket Information\nTickets start from approxim
	ately $54 and are available through Ticketmaster (official tickets) and Vi
	vidSeats (resale tickets). Secure your seats early as this Fourth of July 
	weekend show is expected to sell out! \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \
	nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase 
	tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales are final. 
	Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.\n\
	nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/weird-al-yankovic-bigger-weirder-tour-li
	ve-at-acrisure-amphitheater/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/weird-al-yankovic-bigger-weirder-tour-
	live-at-acrisure-amphitheater/
