SUMMARY:Comedy Cellar Las Vegas (Late)
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260703T213000Z
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at
	 no extra cost to you. \n\nOfficial Tickets\n\nResale Tickets\n\nComedy Ce
	llar Las Vegas brings one of the most legendary names in stand-up comedy t
	o the heart of Las Vegas. Located inside the Rio Hotel & Casino\, this int
	imate comedy club is the West Coast home of New York City’s world-famous C
	omedy Cellar\, the venue that helped launch the careers of comedy icons in
	cluding Dave Chappelle\, Chris Rock\, Jon Stewart\, Ray Romano\, Amy Schum
	er\, Aziz Ansari\, and countless others. \nUnlike traditional comedy shows
	 featuring a single headliner\, Comedy Cellar presents a carefully curated
	 lineup of professional comedians every night. Audiences can expect multip
	le performers during each show\, featuring a mix of nationally touring hea
	dliners\, television favorites\, Comedy Central veterans\, Netflix perform
	ers\, and rising stars from around the world. \nNo two shows are exactly a
	like\, making every visit a unique experience. Surprise drop-in appearance
	s from major comedians performing elsewhere in Las Vegas have become part 
	of the club’s reputation\, giving audiences the chance to see comedy super
	stars in an intimate setting. \nEvent Details\nVenue: Comedy Cellar Las Ve
	gas at Rio Hotel & Casino\nLocation: 3700 W Flamingo Rd\, Las Vegas\, NV 8
	9103\nShow Schedule: Nightly performances throughout the year\nAge Require
	ment: Recommended for audiences 18+ due to mature comedy content \nAbout t
	he Venue\nOpened in 2018\, Comedy Cellar Las Vegas was designed to recreat
	e the atmosphere and energy of the original Greenwich Village club that ha
	s become one of the most respected comedy venues in the world. The 300-sea
	t showroom offers excellent sightlines and an intimate setting that allows
	 audiences to experience stand-up comedy exactly as it was meant to be see
	n: up close and personal. \nThe venue combines the excitement of a Las Veg
	as night out with the authentic feel of a classic New York comedy club. Gu
	ests can enjoy a comfortable showroom environment while watching some of t
	he best comedians working today perform in a setting that encourages spont
	aneity\, crowd interaction\, and unforgettable moments. \nConveniently loc
	ated inside the Rio Hotel & Casino just minutes from the Las Vegas Strip\,
	 the venue offers easy access for both tourists and local comedy fans. \nW
	hat to Expect\nExpect a fast-paced evening featuring multiple comedians pe
	rforming throughout the show. The Comedy Cellar is known for showcasing a 
	wide variety of comedic styles\, from observational humor and storytelling
	 to sharp social commentary\, crowd work\, and cutting-edge stand-up. \nWh
	ether you’re discovering a future comedy star or watching a seasoned veter
	an perfect their craft\, every show delivers the authentic comedy club exp
	erience that has made the Comedy Cellar one of the most respected brands i
	n stand-up comedy. \nFor comedy fans visiting Las Vegas\, Comedy Cellar is
	 widely considered one of the best places in the city to experience live s
	tand-up comedy any night of the week.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/
	comedy-cellar-las-vegas-late/2026-07-03/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/comedy-cellar-las-vegas-late/2026-07-0
	3/
LOCATION:Comedy Cellar Las Vegas at Rio Hotel & Casino\, 3700 W Flamingo Rd
	\, Las Vegas\, NV\, 89103\, United States
