BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://comedycalendar.com/
 wp-content/uploads/2026/03/13_Edp-P1GnWI.png
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://comedycalendar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026
 /03/13_Edp-P1GnWI.png
UID:zfTgGLPSPghEyn0fu3riy
SUMMARY:Benji Brown LIVE at Arlington Improv (4th of July Show)
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260704T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate l
	inks. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. \nAbout the Perfor
	mer\nBenji Brown is an urban comedian setting a new standard in comedy. He
	 toured with Martin Lawrence’s 2018 LIT AF Tour in major arenas across the
	 country and is now the host of Martin Lawrence’s “Yall Know What It Is To
	ur.” He headlined his own “Act Crazy If You Want To” national tour in 2019
	\, making him one of the only urban comedians — alongside Kevin Hart — wit
	h the clout to pull off a solo national tour of that magnitude. \nHis vira
	l character KiKi has garnered over 3 million views\, cementing him as one 
	of the next major urban comedic household names. \nEvent Details\nDate: Sa
	turday\, July 4\, 2026 (Independence Day) \nTime: 7:00 PM (Doors open 6:00
	 PM) \nVenue: Arlington Improv\, 309 Curtis Mathes Way #147\, Arlington\, 
	TX 76018 \nAge Restriction: 18+ \nPrice Range: $20 to $60 per person \nAbo
	ut the Venue\nArlington Improv is located in the Highlands Shopping Center
	 in Arlington\, TX\, across from Torchy’s Tacos. It is an intimate comedy 
	club featuring a full bar and restaurant where guests enjoy world-renowned
	 and local comics in a lively\, up-close setting. \nThe venue also hosts B
	lack Dog Pizza Arcade\, a full-scale free-play retro arcade featuring more
	 than 30 local craft beers. Seating is assigned based on date of purchase.
	 A 2-item food or beverage minimum per person applies once seated\, and th
	ere is an 18% service charge on all checks in the showroom. \nWhat to Expe
	ct\nCelebrate the 4th of July with a night of non-stop laughs as Benji Bro
	wn headlines Arlington Improv. Expect his signature urban humor\, viral ch
	aracter work\, and the high-energy delivery that has made him one of the m
	ost exciting comedians on the national touring circuit. \nThis is an 18+ e
	vent. Doors open at 6:00 PM. Food and beverage service ends approximately 
	45 minutes into the show. All sales are final\, no refunds or exchanges. \
	nTicket Information\nTickets range from $20 to $60 per person. Purchase of
	ficial tickets or find resale options below. \nOfficial TicketsResale Tick
	ets\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/benji-brown-live-at-arlington-impr
	ov-july-fourth/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/benji-brown-live-at-arlington-improv-j
	uly-fourth/
LOCATION:Arlington Improv\, 309 Curtis Mathes Way #147\, Arlington\, TX\, 7
	6018\, United States Of America
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:comedy-calendar
CATEGORIES:Comedy Calendar
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
