SUMMARY:"Weird Al" Yankovic LIVE at The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor
DTSTAMP:20260701T033035Z
DTSTART:20260704T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you
	 purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Ti
	ckets\nResale Tickets \n“Weird Al” Yankovic LIVE at The Colosseum at Caesa
	rs Windsor\nThe legendary “Weird Al” Yankovic is bringing his Bigger & Wei
	rder 2026 Tour to Windsor\, Ontario for an unforgettable all-ages show at 
	The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor on Saturday\, July 4\, 2026. Known for hi
	s hilarious parody songs and outrageous live performances\, Weird Al deliv
	ers a spectacular concert experience packed with comedy\, music\, and non-
	stop entertainment. \nEvent Details\nDate: Saturday\, July 4\, 2026\nTime:
	 8:00 PM (Doors open 7:00 PM)\nVenue: The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor\nAd
	dress: 377 Riverside Drive East\, Windsor\, Ontario\, Canada N9A 7H7\nAge 
	Requirement: All Ages Welcome\nParking: Complimentary parking in attached 
	six-level parking garage \nAbout “Weird Al” Yankovic\n \nWhat to Expect\n\
	nA high-energy\, full-production concert featuring Weird Al’s greatest par
	ody hits\nMultiple costume changes and theatrical set pieces throughout th
	e show\nClassic parodies including “Eat It\,” “Amish Paradise\,” “White & 
	Nerdy\,” and more\nSpecial guest Puddles Pity Party joining the tour\nAn a
	ll-ages family-friendly comedy concert experience\nUnforgettable moments o
	f laughter and musical brilliance\n\nVenue Information\nThe Colosseum at C
	aesars Windsor is one of Canada’s premier entertainment venues\, located a
	t 377 Riverside Drive East in Windsor\, Ontario\, just across the border f
	rom Detroit. The venue features world-class amenities\, complimentary park
	ing\, and easy access from both Canada and the United States. \nTicket Inf
	ormation\nTickets for “Weird Al” Yankovic: Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour star
	t from $118. There is an overall 4-ticket limit per order. Tickets are ava
	ilable through Ticketmaster (official) and VividSeats (resale). \nOfficial
	 Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a c
	ommission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to yo
	u. \nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may
	 be required for entry.\n\nhttps://comedycalendar.com/event/weird-al-yanko
	vic-live-at-the-colosseum-at-caesars-windsor/\n\nFrom Comedy Calendar
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/weird-al-yankovic-live-at-the-colosseu
	m-at-caesars-windsor/
LOCATION:The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor\, 377 Riverside Dr E\, Windsor\, 
	ON\, N9A 7H7\, Canada
