SUMMARY:CCS Nerd Yard Sale III
DTSTAMP:20260701T033036Z
DTSTART:20260718T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:CCS Houston Nerd Yard Sale III — Dig In. Deal Out. Pass It On.\
	nGot shelves full of stuff that deserves a new home? Looking to score fan-
	loved finds at yard-sale prices? CCS Houston Nerd Yard Sale III is back fo
	r a full weekend — two days of clearing\, digging\, dealing\, and connecti
	ng with fellow fans across every fandom and era. \nThis isn’t a convention
	. It’s not a vendor hall. It’s a true community yard sale where real colle
	ctors clear their collections\, real deals get made\, and real conversatio
	ns happen over shared fandoms. \n  \n📅 Date: Saturday–Sunday\, July 18–19\
	, 2026 \n⏰ Time: Saturday: 10AM – 6PM | Sunday: 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9
	700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Pa
	rking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🧺 For Sellers — Clear Your Shelves\, Ma
	ke Some Cash Got boxes of fandom stuff ready to move? Duplicates\, impulse
	 buys\, collections you’ve outgrown? Set up a table\, meet fellow fans\, a
	nd pass your collection on to someone who’ll love it just as much as you d
	id. Perfect for collectors downsizing\, families clearing closets\, and an
	yone who needs to make space. 👉 Apply to be a seller \n  \n🔍 For Shoppers 
	— Dig\, Deal\, Discover Bargain hunters\, this floor is yours. Browse tabl
	es packed with fan-loved finds at yard-sale prices across every fandom and
	 era. You never know what you’ll find — but here’s what might be waiting: 
	\n\n📚 Comics\, manga\, and books\n🎮 Retro games and consoles — NES\, SNES\
	, Sega\, PlayStation classics\, and more\n🧸 Plushies\, pins\, keychains\, 
	and gacha\n🧩 Anime merch\, figures\, and Funkos\n📼 VHS\, vintage media\, a
	nd old-school collectibles\n👕 Fandom fashion and accessories\n🃏 Cards\, to
	ys\, and unexpected gems\n\nPrices are yard-sale friendly. Every table is 
	different. The best finds are the ones you didn’t know you were looking fo
	r. \n  \n👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 All Fandoms. All Ages. Zero Gatekeeping. Bring the whole crew. 
	No pressure. No gatekeeping. Just fans connecting with fans over the thing
	s they love. \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate We’ve secured
	 a special hotel rate exclusively for Nerd Yard Sale III attendees. Book y
	our stay and make it a full weekend. 👉 Book here \n  \nBring your trade bo
	xes. Bring your shopping bags. Bring your inner treasure hunter. CCS Houst
	on Nerd Yard Sale III — July 18 & 19.\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/cc
	s-nerd-yard-sale-iii/\n\nFrom CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-nerd-yard-sale-iii/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT31H
END:VEVENT
