UID:8ZfMgCY4iIshXGGUUjPpc
SUMMARY:CCS Card Show I
DTSTAMP:20260701T033037Z
DTSTART:20260829T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:CCS Card Show I — Every Sport. Every TCG. One Floor.\nHouston\,
	 the hobby comes home. For the first time at CCS\, every major sport and e
	very major TCG land under one roof: sports card collectors\, memorabilia h
	unters\, and TCG players moving cards on the same floor\, the way it shoul
	d be. Modern hits to vintage grails\, sealed wax to graded slabs\, raw sin
	gles to game-used pieces. Buy\, sell\, trade\, grade. This is the room. \n
	  \n📅 Date: August 29-30\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet 
	St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n🔥 
	Event Highlights 🔥 \n⚾ The Ultimate Sports Card & Memorabilia Marketplace 
	\nExplore vendors dedicated to sports cards\, high-end memorabilia\, and r
	are collectibles from baseball\, football\, basketball\, and more. If you’
	re hunting for a signed rookie card\, vintage set\, or exclusive autograph
	\, this is THE place to level up your collection. \n  \n🃏 Trading Card Gam
	e Extravaganza 🃏 \nWe’re also featuring top TCG vendors offering a treasur
	e trove of Pokémon\, Yu-Gi-Oh!\, Magic: The Gathering\, One Piece\, Lorcan
	a\, and more! Chase that elusive rare pull or build your deck for your nex
	t tournament\, you’ll find the best deals on booster packs\, graded single
	s\, sealed products\, and Japanese imports. \n  \n💼 Vendors Wanted \nGot a
	 table’s worth to move? Guest vendors are welcome at Card Show I. The pers
	on across the table is a fan like you. Claim your spot 👉🏻 https://forms.gle
	/sZdrRxHkEXM69kbN6 \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In Your Rate\nEnjoy 
	a special rate of $79/night — ****2 Queens at TownePlace Suites\, only 15 
	minutes away from the action! 👉 https://www.marriott.com/event-reservation
	s/reservation-link.mi?id=1767823967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n  \nHouston
	’s first CCS Card Show. Every sport\, every TCG\, one floor. Pull up.\n\nh
	ttps://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-card-show-i/\n\nFrom CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/ccs-card-show-i/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT31H
END:VEVENT
