UID:8QGCLm6IfQHR8DVvLmwR2
SUMMARY:Demon Slayer Mini Con
DTSTAMP:20260701T033037Z
DTSTART:20260919T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:🔥 Calling all Demon Slayer Corps members\, Hashira-in-training\
	, and Tanjiro fans**!** 🔥\nFrom Mizunoto beginners to seasoned Hashira\, m
	asters of Sun Breathing to the loyal members of the Zenitsu-squad\, Demon 
	Slayer Mini Con is your next mission! CCS Houston is hosting a one-day Tot
	al Concentration event for every slayer who lives for the Hinokami Kagura\
	, the intensity of the Upper Rank battles\, and the bond between friends. 
	\nJoin the Corps for a day packed with Nichirin-grade marketplace finds\, 
	Cosplay haoris\, and Blood Demon Art energy\, all in a fan-first space whe
	re no one is left in the Final Selection alone. \nSteel your heart\, grab 
	your Kasugai Crow\, and let’s set our hearts ablaze together ⚔️✨ \n  \n🗓️ Da
	te & Time: Saturday\, Sept 19\, 2026 | 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bisso
	nnet St\, #1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + FREE Parking \n  \n👘
	 Demon Slayer Cosplay Showcase + Demon Face-Off (2 PM)\nPrepare for a Hash
	ira-level showdown in a dramatic pose-off against our “demon.” The crowd’s
	 roar will determine who survives the night and claims victory. \n  \n🎴 Ni
	chirin Sword Pose-Off (3PM)\nEven without a uniform\, your spirit can burn
	 bright! Grab a Nichirin blade\, take the stage\, and unleash your most ic
	onic Breathing Style pose for a chance to win a prize. \n  \n🎮 Demon Slaye
	r: Hinokami Chronicles Free-Play Zone (All Day)\nJump into the action in o
	ur gaming area! Join free play sessions on the Demon Slayer: The Hinokami 
	Chronicles video game and challenge fellow slayers to a dueling trial. \n 
	 \nDemon Slayer Trivia (3:30 PM)\nOnly those with the sharpest focus will 
	survive this mental trial and earn their rank as a true scholar of the ser
	ies. \n  \n🎨 Nezuko’s Box DIY Craft Station (All Day)\nChannel your inner 
	Urokodaki to construct a miniature wooden-style carrier using paper\, char
	ms\, and markers. Open to all ages! \n  \n🔥 Demon Slayer Artist Alley\nWan
	der through a marketplace filled with hand-forged treasures and fandom col
	lectibles\, including custom Nichirin charms\, Demon Slayer-inspired print
	s\, and talismans for the next mission\, our Artist Alley features the mos
	t talented creators in the Corps. \n🔥 Want to create something special for
	 Demon Slayer fans? \n🔗 Host activities\, workshops\, or panels → https://
	forms.gle/q2nCKsZ6FEVZBgqW9 \n🔗 Volunteer Sign-Up → https://forms.gle/15zM
	GTqZPSGKjGdy6 \n🔗 Vendor Applications → https://tinyurl.com/HoustonVendors
	\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/demon-slayer-mini-con/\n\nFrom CCS Hous
	ton
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/demon-slayer-mini-con/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H
END:VEVENT
